These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | weightlifting | skiing | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, onion, strawberry
1. the person eating onion is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | asparagus | strawberry | onion |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, video-games, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | video-games | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, funk, dubstep
1. the fan of funk is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | dubstep | funk |

